{"thig7.2:0.1":"Therigatha 7.2 ","thig7.2:0.2":"Sattakanipata ","thig7.2:0.3":"Calatherigatha ","thig7.2:1.1":"“Satim upatthapetvana, ","thig7.2:1.2":"bhikkhuni bhavitindriya; ","thig7.2:1.3":"Pativijjhi padam santam, ","thig7.2:1.4":"sankharupasamam sukham”. ","thig7.2:2.1":"“Kam nu uddissa mundasi, ","thig7.2:2.2":"samani viya dissasi; ","thig7.2:2.3":"Na ca rocesi pasande, ","thig7.2:2.4":"kimidam carasi momuha”. ","thig7.2:3.1":"“Ito bahiddha pasanda, ","thig7.2:3.2":"ditthiyo upanissita; ","thig7.2:3.3":"Na te dhammam vijananti, ","thig7.2:3.4":"na te dhammassa kovida. ","thig7.2:4.1":"Atthi sakyakule jato, ","thig7.2:4.2":"buddho appatipuggalo; ","thig7.2:4.3":"So me dhammamadesesi, ","thig7.2:4.4":"ditthinam samatikkamam. ","thig7.2:5.1":"Dukkham dukkhasamuppadam, ","thig7.2:5.2":"Dukkhassa ca atikkamam; ","thig7.2:5.3":"Ariyam catthangikam maggam, ","thig7.2:5.4":"Dukkhupasamagaminam. ","thig7.2:6.1":"Tassaham vacanam sutva, ","thig7.2:6.2":"viharim sasane rata; ","thig7.2:6.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thig7.2:6.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thig7.2:7.1":"Sabbattha vihata nandi, ","thig7.2:7.2":"tamokhandho padalito; ","thig7.2:7.3":"Evam janahi papima, ","thig7.2:7.4":"nihato tvamasi antaka”. ","thig7.2:8.1":"… Cala theri …. "}